{"lemma":"طِمِرُّ","slug":"طِمِرُّ","root":"ط.م.ر","root_slug":"ط-م-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-م-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":8,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":10},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27078","n27079","n27082","n27083","n27084","n27090"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%90%D9%85%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to rise, to leap upwards, to spring","tags":["obsolete"],"examples":[{"text":"a. 1059, by Abū al-ʿAlāʾ Maʿarri\nوَلَيْسَ الطِمِرُّ سِوَى مَا طَمَر\nwa-laysa ṭ-ṭimirru siwā mā ṭamar","english":"There is nothing swift that does not leap."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become inflated, to become swollen, to intumesce","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bury, to landfill, to embed, to inter, to slam","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fold up, to roll up","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to groom, to currycomb","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lock up, to put into the silo (مَطْمُورَة (maṭmūra))","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of طَمَرَ (ṭamara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of طَمِرَ (ṭamira) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"tatter, worn-out garment","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"swift, fleet, of active legs","tags":["obsolete"],"examples":[{"text":"a. 1059, by Abū al-ʿAlāʾ Maʿarri\nوَلَيْسَ الطِمِرُّ سِوَى مَا طَمَر\nwa-laysa ṭ-ṭimirru siwā mā ṭamar","english":"There is nothing swift that does not leap."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27078","headword_ar":"طَمَرَ","root":"Tmr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TamorN","text_ar":"طَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He buried"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, K) a corpse,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he hid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, Msb, K,) a thing, (Msb,) or wheat, in a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTomuwrap","text_ar":"مَطْمُورَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) or himself, or his goods, (A, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a place where he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they, could not be known."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He filled"},{"kind":"text","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTomuwrap","text_ar":"مَطْمُورَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He filled up"},{"kind":"text","text":"a well. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Az heard a man of 'Okeyl say of a stallion-camel that had covered a female,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qado TamarahaA","text_ar":"قَدْ طَمَرَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He inserted the whole of his veretrum into her;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as is indicated by the context]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu lakaviyru AlT~umuwri","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَكَثِيرُ الطُّمُورِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and thus one says of a man, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is one who compresses much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA. [See also 4.])       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tamara","text_ar":"طَمَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He built."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) And [hence] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abiyhi","text_ar":"اَبِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yaTomuru EalaY miTomaAri","text_ar":"هُوَ يَطْمُرُ عَلَى مِطْمَارِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K, in the latter of which the verb is omitted,) meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He imitates the actions of his father:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he resembles his father in make and disposition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tamara","text_ar":"طَمَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TumuwrN","text_ar":"طُمُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TamorN","text_ar":"طَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TimaArN","text_ar":"طِمَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA, in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TamAr","text_ar":"طَمار"},{"kind":"text","text":") and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TamaraAnN","text_ar":"طَمَرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He leaped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he leaped downwards:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upwards"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into, the sky"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (A, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did what resembled leaping"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upwards"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into, the sky"},{"kind":"text","text":"); (S;) thus does a horse; and the [bird called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoyal","text_ar":"اَخْيَل"},{"kind":"text","text":", in flying. (S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tamara fiY Alr~akiy~api","text_ar":"طَمَرَ فِى الرَّكِيَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TamorN","text_ar":"طَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TumuwrN","text_ar":"طُمُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He leaped into the well, from the top of it to the bottom."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [It is said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tamara","text_ar":"طَمَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rose, high:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"descended, low."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [But perhaps it is a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tumira","text_ar":"طُمِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTomuwrN","text_ar":"مَطْمُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tamara fiY AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"طَمَرَ فِى الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TumuwrN","text_ar":"طُمُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went away into,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in, the country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became absent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he absented,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed, himself."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tamara","text_ar":"طَمَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a wound,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became inflated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swollen."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tamirato yaduhu","text_ar":"طَمِرَتْ يَدُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the verb in this case being of the class of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHa","text_ar":"فَرِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His arm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hand, became swollen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and inflated."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tumira fiY vadoYi AlmaroA^api","text_ar":"طُمِرَ فِى ثَدْىِ المَرْاَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The woman's breast became swollen."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tumira fiY Dirosihi","text_ar":"طُمِرَ فِى ضِرْسِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pain became excited in his tooth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his lateral,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"molar, tooth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) the verb in this phrase [and in that next preceding] is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuniYa","text_ar":"عُنِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","A","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27079","headword_ar":"طمّر","root":"Tmr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTomiyrN","text_ar":"تَطْمِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made"},{"kind":"text","text":"his building"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"high."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawaY","text_ar":"طَوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He folded"},{"kind":"text","text":"a written paper &c.; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rolled up"},{"kind":"text","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuwmaAr","text_ar":"طُومَار"},{"kind":"text","text":", or scroll: and (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the Creator)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made"},{"kind":"text","text":"the limbs, or shanks, of an animal,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compact,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"round; as though rolled up like scrolls"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, K, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tum~irato","text_ar":"طُمِّرَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a verse of Kaab Ibn-Zuheyr, [referring to a wild she-ass, or to her legs,] means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they were, rendered compact in make;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rounded, as though rolled up like as are"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawaAmiyr","text_ar":"طَوَامِير"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scrolls"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He let down a curtain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tam~aruwA buyuwtahumo","text_ar":"طَمَّرُوا بُيُوتَهُمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They let down their curtains over their doors."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n27082","headword_ar":"طِمْرٌ","root":"Tmr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An old and worn-out garment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, Mgh, Msb, K:) this is the meaning commonly known: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an old and worn-out"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garment of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisaA='","text_ar":"كِسَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not of wool:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, A, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TumoruwrN","text_ar":"طُمْرُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (Ibn-'Abbád, O, K:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTomaArN","text_ar":"اَطْمَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O, Msb, K,) the only pl. form. (Sb, TA.)       -A2-  See also the next paragraph. [Freytag has assigned to this word, as on the authority of the K, three meanings which the K assigns to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TumoruwrN","text_ar":"طُمْرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","A","O","Mgh","Msb","K","TA","IAar"]},{"entry_id":"n27083","headword_ar":"طِمِرٌّ","root":"Tmr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TimorN","text_ar":"طِمْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TimorirN","text_ar":"طِمْرِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TumoruwrN","text_ar":"طُمْرُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TimoriyrN","text_ar":"طِمْرِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uTomur~N","text_ar":"اُطْمُرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) A horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of excitement"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotafiz~N","text_ar":"مُسْتَفِزٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so accord. to my copies of the S, as though for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotafiz~N nafosahu","text_ar":"مُسْتَفِزٌّ نَفْسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or probably a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotafaz~N","text_ar":"مُسْتَفَزٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to leap and run:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O: [accord. to my copies of the former,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotafiz~N lilowavobi waAlEadowi","text_ar":"مُسْتَفِزٌّ لِلْوَثْبِ وَالعَدْوِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": in the O,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotafiz~u Alwatobi waAlEadowi","text_ar":"مُسْتَفِزُّ الوَتْبِ وَالعَدْوِ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or, accord. to AO,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compact"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in make:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) and (O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fleet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swift, and excellent, horse:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) and the first,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that leaps much;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dibir~N","text_ar":"ضِبِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dbr","text_ar":"ضبر"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TumoruwrN","text_ar":"طُمْرُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longlegged, and light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ready,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of preparation, for running:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) the fem."},{"kind":"page_break","n":1880},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Timir~apN","text_ar":"طِمِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied metaphorically by a poet to a she-ass as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehement in running."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makaAnN Timir~N","text_ar":"مَكَانٌ طِمِرٌّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A high place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n27084","headword_ar":"طُمُرٌّ","root":"Tmr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tum~arN","text_ar":"طُمَّرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n27090","headword_ar":"طُمَّرٌ","root":"Tmr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSolN","text_ar":"اَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tim~aworN","text_ar":"طِمَّوْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, K:) so the former signifies in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA^arud~an~ahu A_ilaY Tum~arihi","text_ar":"لَاَرُدَّنَّهُ اـِلَى طُمَّرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will assuredly reduce him to the utmost point,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"degree, to which he can be reduced:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see a similar phrase voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSolN","text_ar":"اَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) ―         -b2-  And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN Tum~aru $ar~K","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ طُمَّرُ شَرٍّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is evil in the utmost degree."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drn","text_ar":"درن"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anota fiY Tum~arika Al~a*iY kunota fiyhi","text_ar":"اَنْتَ فِى طُمَّرِكَ الَّذِى كُنْتَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in copies of the K and in the TA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tumur~ika","text_ar":"طُمُرِّكَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in the O,) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY gir~atika wajaholika","text_ar":"فِى غِرَّتِكَ وَجَهْلِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou art in thy state of inexperience and ignorance in which thou wast"},{"kind":"text","text":"formerly]: (O, K:) but [SM says] the right reading is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY garobika","text_ar":"فى غَرْبِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in thy"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharpness, and briskness, liveliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sprightliness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"in some copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eazomika wajahodika","text_ar":"عَزْمِكَ وَجَهْدِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and in some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euroyika wajahodika","text_ar":"عُرْيِكَ وَجَهْدِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which are both mistranscriptions: (TA:) a saying mentioned by Fr. (O.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}